A massive medieval castle at dawn with knights on horseback riding out through the gates in all directions across rolling hills, each knight carrying a different colored banner streaming behind them, the castle's towers built from interlocking database cylinders and server components, misty atmosphere with golden light breaking through clouds, birds-eye view showing the strategic dispersal pattern of the knights across a vast landscape of interconnected villages and pathways, dramatic sense of an empire expanding its influence through trusted emissaries.
